text: Jørgen Ravn (9 January 1884 - 1 December 1962) was a Danish gymnast. He competed in the men's team, Swedish system event at the 1912 Summer Olympics, winning a silver medal. ==References== Category:1884 births Category:1962 deaths Category:Danish male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Denmark Category:Gymnasts at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:People from Guldborgsund Municipality Category:Olympic silver medalists for Denmark Category:Olympic medalists in gymnastics Category:Medalists at the 1912 Summer Olympics
